  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Write the two equations",
      "content": "The two rope pieces total $123$ inches:<br/><br/>$$x+y=123$$<br/><br/>The value of $x$ is $3$ more than $5$ times $y$:<br/><br/>$$x=5y+3$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for the other piece",
      "content": "Substitute $x=5y+3$ into the total:<br/><br/>$$(5y+3)+y=123$$<br/>$$6y+3=123$$<br/>$$6y=120$$<br/>$$y=20$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Find the requested length",
      "content": "Use $x=5y+3$:<br/><br/>$$x=5(20)+3=103$$<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>D</strong>."
    }
  ]
